title: Movies of the Millenium
description:
Chris is ready to launch a new show. A radio host in Charlotte tries to cancel Fred Toucher. A listener asks KFC why Big Cat and Dave Portnoy are copying Kirk Minihane. Kirk addresses his tweet from yesterday where he saw a man that looked like his father. We add to Kirk's Hall of Fame, Chris Klemmer has phone sex & much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
